Detailed Description

ATOProgeny class was taken out because it is the same class with a few extra properties.

this class and the old ATOContam have been "unioned"

class ATOProgeny { public: char chemname[80]; char casid[80]; int numtimes; char parenname[80]; char parencasid[80]; ATOTimePeriod **times;
